  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a fondue pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onions and cook until they are translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Stir in the green olives, chicken broth, saffron threads, and smoked paprika.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10 minutes.",
    "While the paella is cooking, prepare the agemono topping by following the package instructions.",
